{"tid":372314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不滿友人向男友介紹女性 女會計師帶磚上酒店尋仇","createTime":"2017-08-24T08:51:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T12:56:26.000Z","uid":122,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f06c87db5fe0a25a3548a79843d6723a62c1dce8","tid":372314,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T08:51:21.000Z","msg":"<strong>不滿友人向男友介紹女性 女會計師帶磚上酒店尋仇</strong><br />\n<br />\n30歲的女會計師稱不滿男友人向其男友介紹女性，於是在6月12日的早上，先於尖沙嘴街頭拾來磚頭，再乘的士到位於將軍澳的香港九龍東皇冠假日酒店房內，打算找男友人算帳，最終與房內的男友爭執，事件最終驚動警方。<br />\n<br />\n女會計師葉碧霞原被控一項管有攻擊性武器罪，控方今撤控，改以簽保守行為處理，被告獲准以1,000元守行為一年。裁判官告誡被告：「今次好彩，下次做嘢前要三思」。<br />\n<br />\n據控方案情指，被告當日到達房間後，手持磚頭與男友發生激烈衝突，因而有人報警。被告於警誡下指，涉事的男友人已於警方抵達現場前離開。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c624ad513ea3ead983991815593bdb506700ed49","tid":372314,"uid":34498,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T08:54:30.000Z","msg":"仲話會計師 讀咁撚多書把撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4dd1e135b91dab0de764205e473db632f8dd20","tid":372314,"uid":38539,"like":90,"dislike":0,"score":90,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T09:01:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲話會計師 讀咁撚多書把撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n讀會計就係去算帳"},{"pid":"d2196460f4575807aa5057b34c36daab86489da8","tid":372314,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T09:02:35.000Z","msg":"睇完心諗一句：做乜鳩！？"},{"pid":"0477b66710a2828a1654f74b397c2d03792ebd77","tid":372314,"uid":1082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T09:03:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲話會計師 讀咁撚多書把撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n讀會計就係去算帳</blockquote><br />\n你啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"